==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Prithee
<hw>Prith"ee</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>interj.</pos> <def>A corruption of
<xex>pray thee</xex>; <as>as, I <ex>prithee</ex></as>; generally used
without <it>I</it>.</def><-- = pray (interj.). See I pray, under pray,
v.i. --> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>What was that scream for, I <qex>prithee</qex>?</q>
<rj><qau>L'Estrange.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Prithee</qex>, tell me, Dimple-chin.</q> <rj><qau>E. C.
Stedman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Prittle-prattle</ent>⟦br⟧
